The configuration util is currently a work in progress.

In order to run the coLinux configurator, you need to install python
2.3. Windows users can use the installer from www.python.org. 

    http://www.python.org/ftp/python/2.3.3/Python-2.3.3.exe
    
The configuration util also depends on wxpython which can be obtained 
from http://www.wxpython.org:

    http://prdownloads.sourceforge.net/wxpython/wxPythonWIN32-2.5.1.5-Py23.exe
